<section role="region" aria-labelledby="featured-content" class="page-section--container">
  <header role="section title" class="page-section--header">
    <div class="section-tag-border"></div>
    <h6 class="section--tag text--inverse">Featured Content</h6>
  </header>
   <div class="page-section--body">
    <h2 class="title">CureAccelerator Featured Users And Projects</h2>
    <p class="text">CureAccelerator, created by Cures Within Reach to scale up repurposing collaborations to drive more treatments to more patients more quickly. Cures Within Reach has supported the creation of 12 repurposed therapies either being used clinically or in larger Phase II clinical trials.</p>
